OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,FTeaching staff at a Northumberland
OL,7,Fhigh school have again walked out over
OL,8,Fpoor pupil behaviour. Union members at
OL,9,FHaydon Bridge High School were on the
OL,10,Fpicket line amid claims management
OL,11,Fhave failed to act on concerns.
OL,13,FThree days of strike action began on
OL,14,FTuesday 31 March, with a further nine
OL,15,Fdays planned to follow later on, the
OL,16,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service
OL,17,Freports.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
