PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for the National
OL,7,FEducation Union said: "Support Staff
OL,8,Fand Teachers at Haydon Bridge High
OL,9,FSchool want to have a safe system of
OL,10,Fpupil behaviour in place and working.
OL,11,FThey put the safety of all pupils at
OL,12,Fthe top of their list of priorities.
OL,14,F"For almost two years, staff at the
OL,15,Fschool have been pleading with the
OL,16,FHead Teacher and Governors to
OL,17,Fimplement an effective pupil behaviour
OL,18,Fmanagement policy and procedures.
OL,19,FDespite the creation of a new pupil
OL,20,Fbehaviour policy on paper, it has
OL,21,Fremained largely on paper.
OL,26,@oD@WOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,F"The leadership of the school have not
OL,7,Fshown a commitment to implementing the
OL,8,Fnew behaviour policy. There have been
OL,9,Fsudden and unexpected changes to the
OL,10,Fbehaviour policy without any
OL,11,Fconsultation with the frontline staff.
OL,13,F"Our members want to see the school
OL,14,Fstarting to succeed rather than fail."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
