PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,FA recent Ofsted inspection, carried
OL,7,Fout in January and published last
OL,8,Fweek, recommended that the school be
OL,9,Fplaced in special measures. The report
OL,10,Fstated: "The persons responsible for
OL,11,Fleading, managing or governing the
OL,12,Fschool are not demonstrating the
OL,13,Fcapacity to secure the necessary
OL,14,Fimprovement in the school.
OL,16,F"Leaders and governors know there are
OL,17,Fmany areas of the school that need to
OL,18,Fbe improved. However, they have not
OL,19,Facted swiftly or effectively enough to
OL,20,Faddress these concerns.
OL,26,@rD@IOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,F"Governors do not ensure that all of
OL,7,Ftheir statutory duties are met. They
OL,8,Fdo not challenge leaders sufficiently
OL,9,Fwell. School leaders do not have the
OL,10,Fcapacity to bring about the necessary
OL,11,Fimprovements.
OL,13,F"Leaders and governors have not acted
OL,14,Fquickly enough to address weaknesses
OL,15,Fand improve pupils' experiences at
OL,16,Fschool."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
