PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,FDespite the strike action, the school
OL,7,Fremains open to all pupils except
OL,8,Fthose in Year 9. School leaders have
OL,9,Fexpressed disappointment at the
OL,10,Fwalkout.
OL,12,FThis is not the first time teachers
OL,13,Fhave gone on strike at Haydon Bridge
OL,14,FHigh School. Action took place in
OL,15,FDecember last year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
