PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Northumberland
OL,7,FCounty Council said: "School leaders
OL,8,Fand governors are extremely
OL,9,Fdisappointed to see this industrial
OL,10,Faction taking place. We have been
OL,11,Fworking with staff and their Unions to
OL,12,Fidentify issues and have engaged in a
OL,13,Fnumber of actions.
OL,15,F"Improvement plans are underway with
OL,16,Ffurther co-produced plans for
OL,17,Fimprovement recently introduced. We
OL,18,Fhad hoped that unions may pause their
OL,19,Faction to allow this improvement to
OL,20,Fbecome embedded.
OL,26,@oD@VOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,F"We are committed to build on this
OL,7,Fbase to rapidly address the remaining
OL,8,Fissues. School leaders and governors
OL,9,Fwould want to express thanks to the
OL,10,Fschool staff, students and parents
OL,11,Fcontinuing to support the school and
OL,12,Ftheir combined work in making it
OL,13,Fimprove."
OL,15,FCouncillor Guy Renner-Thompson,
OL,16,FCabinet member for Children and Young
OL,17,FPeople at Northumberland County
OL,18,FCouncil, added: "I share the
OL,19,Fdisappointment of school leaders and
OL,20,Fgovernors that industrial action is
OL,21,Fgoing ahead.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]zD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1775063147
OL,3,CTeachers continue strike action over
OL,4,Cpoor pupil behaviour at high school
OL,6,F"The unions shared a multi-point list
OL,7,Fwhere they wanted improvements. I
OL,8,Fbelieve each point has been actioned
OL,9,Fand yet they are still striking-
OL,10,F despite improvements being made as
OL,11,Fnoted by Ofsted in their recent report.
OL,13,F"Ofsted did state that the school was
OL,14,Fcalm and that bullying was not a
OL,15,Fconcern. This is a time to pull
OL,16,Ftogether to support the school and the
OL,17,Fcommunity, and I implore and welcome
OL,18,Fall parties committed to doing so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
